 The family of a Lagos-based chef and CEO of I Luv Desserts, Peju Ugboma want justice served. According to an autopsy, carried out by the family, late Peju died after a Fibroid operation left her bleeding internally. The hospital has been accused of focusing on other things and intentionally ignoring the complaints of Peju and a recommendation from a doctor in the UK. View this post on Instagram A post shared by Olorisupergal (@olorisupergal)